      <div class="columns is-centered">
         <div class="column is-8 animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeIn">
            <div class="content">
               <p>We are committed to investing in each other through
               on-the-job training opportunities.  We are devoted to our
               families which includes maintaining a healthy work/life balance.
               We are passionate about giving back to our community and our
               planet through volunteer events.  Vihanti Digital Services even
               donates a percentage of all profits to the causes that our
               employees care about most.  Above all, we treat each other and
               our customers with respect and integrity.</p>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

   <section class="section is-fullwidth is-variant1">
      <div class="columns is-centered">
         <div class="column is-8">
            <div class="content">
               <h2 class="title">Our Values</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="columns">
               <div class="column">
                  <div class="box content animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeInLeft">
                     <div class="level">
                        <div class="level-left">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <h3 class="subtitle has-text-dark">Creativity</h3>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-right">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <span class="icon is-large">
                                 <i class="fas fa-lightbulb fa-2x"></i>
                              </span>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <p>We challenge each other to think outside the box.  We
                     enjoy learning new things and pushing the limits of
                     innovation.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="column">
                  <div class="box content animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeInUp">
                     <div class="level">
                        <div class="level-left">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <h3 class="subtitle has-text-dark">Integrity</h3>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-right">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <span class="icon is-large">
                                 <i class="fas fa-award fa-2x"></i>
                              </span>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <p>We do the right thing even when it costs us.  This
                     includes being honest with each other and with our
                     customers.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="column">
                  <div class="box content animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeInRight">
                     <div class="level">
                        <div class="level-left">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <h3 class="subtitle has-text-dark">Teamwork</h3>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-right">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <span class="icon is-large">
                                 <i class="fas fa-comments fa-2x"></i>
                              </span>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <p>We work better together.  We appreciate the strengths of
                     our team mates and help each other to be more than we could
                     imagine.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

   <section class="perks section is-fullwidth is-variant2">
      <div class="columns is-centered">
         <div class="column is-8">
            <div class="content">
               <h2 class="title">Our Perks</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="columns">
               <div class="column">
                  <div class="box content animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeInLeft">
                     <div class="level">
                        <div class="level-left">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <h3 class="subtitle has-text-dark">Training</h3>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-right">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <span class="icon is-large">
                                 <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher fa-2x"></i>
                              </span>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <p>We provide on-the-job training to help you take your
                     career to the next level.  Learn the latest technology from
                     those with decades of industry experience.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="column">
                  <div class="box content animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeInUp">
                     <div class="level">
                        <div class="level-left">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <h3 class="subtitle has-text-dark">Relationships</h3>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-right">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <span class="icon is-large">
                                 <i class="fas fa-users fa-2x"></i>
                              </span>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <p>We take time to get to know each other, because we believe
                     that work doesn’t need to feel like work.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div class="column">
                  <div class="box content animated no-opacity" data-animated="fadeInRight">
                     <div class="level">
                        <div class="level-left">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <h3 class="subtitle has-text-dark">Flexible Time Off</h3>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-right">
                           <div class="level-item">
                              <span class="icon is-large">
                                 <i class="fas fa-home fa-2x"></i>
                              </span>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <p>Our time off policy ensures that you have space for
                     recharging with family and friends.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

   <section class="section is-fullwidth">
      <div class="columns is-centered">
         <div class="column is-8">
            Are you intrigued?  <a href="/contact.html">Contact us!</a>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>
{% endblock %}

